{"tid":2428217,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★立法會研究指本地自置居所比率：35歲以下 7.6%；60歲以上 41%","createTime":"2021-03-01T11:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T07:14:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8238fe0551760541dc6ccc8f1ac1003ebefc4ca0","tid":2428217,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"研究報告稱，自置居所可為社會帶來明顯效益，包括培養社會歸屬感和促進社會政治穩定。然而在土地嚴重短缺、置業負擔能力下降情況下，35歲以下的年輕世代，在整體自置居所戶主比例，自1997年的22.1%，大幅收縮至2019年7.6%。相反的是，60歲及以上的年長戶主比例是41%，較1997年的21%相應升近1倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2889497/立法會研究指本地自置居所比率跌至五成%E3%80%80創廿年新低?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2889497%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E8%87%AA%E7%BD%AE%E5%B1%85%E6%89%80%E6%AF%94%E7%8E%87%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%25E3%2580%2580%E5%89%B5%E5%BB%BF%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1%2F56hpy2SSQtx6ElJ%2BvIbMI%3D&h=ad49b7d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2889497/立法會研究指本地自置居所比率跌至五成%E3%80%80創廿年新低?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"259d264d9190a7198836c97d81f3c7d2e3a95e65","tid":2428217,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANGr2GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANGr2GX.png&h=017d56af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53deb4dcb878948da28a7d00592d808037d2b347","tid":2428217,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6ed44f58144902b54125a